<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,326,1980,2004]" pageId="77" pageNumber="78">Etymology</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
The species name is a Latin participle (
<emphasis box="[779,980,1981,2004]" italics="true" pageId="77" pageNumber="78">truncatus, -a, -um</emphasis>
= truncated).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
